%H A282715 Julien Leroy, Michel Rigo, Manon Stipulanti, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1705.10065">Counting Subwords Occurrences in Base-b Expansions</a>, arXiv:1705.10065 [math.CO], 2017.
